{"tid":1848771,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國專家指需等一個月才能拿到新型肺炎疫苗株","createTime":"2020-01-28T15:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T18:58:52.000Z","uid":125193,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c35583f7e001dba645bca33b9e9fb9dabba06a83","tid":1848771,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505341-20200128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505341-20200128.htm&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGVSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=6a9438a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505341-20200128.htm&h=0aceb44f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505341-20200128.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n國家衛健委高級別專家組成員李蘭娟表示，國家衛健委高級別專家組成員李蘭娟表示，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">距離製備新型肺炎疫苗已經很近，但需要等一個月才能拿到疫苗株，檢查檢測則需要等半個月，另外至少審批一個半月。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李蘭娟接受央視直播訪問時說，昨日新增1700多宗確診病例屬於預期之中，因為武漢封城之前，從當地輸出各個省份的感染者，通過第二、第三代傳播後，目前處於發病高峰期。<br />\n<br />\n李蘭娟又指，病毒除了經呼吸道傳播，還可以通過接觸傳播，病人的飛沫可能影響環境，她建議民衆勤洗手，切斷傳播途徑。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她表示非常重視沒有病徵的患者，雖然對預防疫情帶來難度，但現時可以透過大數據，監測每個人的流動情況，以發現和控制傳染源。"},{"pid":"c4f27260466ced883c4c6c10cd03de8bb1630cd5","tid":1848771,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"三峽大壩....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b8cf2121383472ec41bdbbd82f554ec8e1d188","tid":1848771,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6d7b90fcc8d741c4b665522b16d946b9311e63","tid":1848771,"uid":271894,"like"